  <br />
  <a href="https://assets.documentcloud.org/documents/5752908/Testimoy-Michael-Cohen-2-27-19-the-Oversight.txt">Michael Cohen's opening statement to the House Oversight Committee (Text)</a>
</noscript>
</aside><div class="story-share ">
